/* SQL ID : ExamDAO.listExamByInsRef 설 명 : 중간/기말 대체 목록 조회 */ WITH M AS ( /* 과제 */ SELECT 'ASMNT' AS STARE_TYPE , '과제' AS TYPE_NM , A.ASMT_ID AS CODE , A.ASMT_TTL AS TTL , 'Y' AS SUBMIT_YN , A.SEND_START_DTTM AS SYMD , A.SEND_END_DTTM AS EYMD , (SELECT COUNT(B.STD_ID) FROM TB_LMS_ASMT_SBMSN B JOIN TB_LMS_ATNDLC_SBJCT C ON B.STD_ID = C.STD_ID AND C.ATNDLC_STSCD ='S' WHERE B.ASMT_ID = A.ASMT_ID AND B.SBMSN_STSCD <> 'NO' AND C.SBJCT_ID = A.SBJCT_ID) AS JOIN_CNT , CASE WHEN A.ASMT_CTGRCD = 'SUBS' THEN (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM TB_LMS_ATNDLC_SBJCT WHERE SBJCT_ID = A.SBJCT_ID AND ATNDLC_STSCD = 'S' AND STD_ID IN (SELECT STD_ID FROM TB_LMS_EXAM_STARE WHERE REEXAMYN = 'Y' AND EXAM_ID = (SELECT EXAM_ID FROM TB_LMS_EXAM_BSC WHERE EXAM_SBST_REF_ID = A.ASMT_ID AND DELYN = 'N'))) ELSE (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM TB_LMS_ATNDLC_SBJCT WHERE SBJCT_ID = A.SBJCT_ID AND ATNDLC_STSCD = 'S') END AS TOTAL_CNT , (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM TB_LMS_ASMT_MTL_EVL WHERE ASMT_ID = A.ASMT_ID) AS EVAL_CNT , A.EXT_SEND_DTTM AS LATE_DTTM , A.MRK_OYN AS MRK_OYN FROM TB_LMS_ASMT AS A WHERE A.DELYN = 'N' /* 토론 */ UNION ALL SELECT 'FORUM' AS STARE_TYPE , '토론' AS TYPE_NM , A.DSCS_ID AS CODE , A.DSCS_TTL AS TTL , 'Y' AS SUBMIT_YN , A.DSCS_SDTTM AS SYMD , A.DSCS_EDTTM AS EYMD , (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM (SELECT DISTINCT S.STD_ID FROM TB_LMS_ATNDLC_SBJCT AS S JOIN TB_LMS_DSCS_ATCL AS B ON S.STD_ID = B.STD_ID AND S.ATNDLC_STSCD = 'S' LEFT OUTER JOIN TB_LMS_DSCS_CMNT AS C ON S.STD_ID = C.STD_ID WHERE S.SBJCT_ID = A.SBJCT_ID AND (B.DELYN = 'N' OR C.DELYN = 'N') AND B.DSCS_ID = A.DSCS_ID OR C.DSCS_ID = A.DSCS_ID) AS T) AS JOIN_CNT , CASE WHEN A.DSCS_TYCD = 'SUBS' THEN (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM TB_LMS_ATNDLC_SBJCT WHERE SBJCT_ID = A.SBJCT_ID AND ATNDLC_STSCD = 'S' AND STD_ID IN (SELECT STD_ID FROM TB_LMS_EXAM_STARE WHERE REEXAMYN = 'Y' AND EXAM_ID = (SELECT EXAM_ID FROM TB_LMS_EXAM_BSC WHERE EXAM_SBST_REF_ID = A.DSCS_ID AND DELYN = 'N'))) ELSE (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM TB_LMS_ATNDLC_SBJCT WHERE SBJCT_ID = A.SBJCT_ID AND ATNDLC_STSCD = 'S') END AS TOTAL_CNT , (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM TB_LMS_DSCS_MTL_EVL WHERE DSCS_ID = A.DSCS_ID GROUP BY STD_ID) AS T) AS EVAL_CNT , '' AS LATE_DTTM , A.MRK_OYN AS MRK_OYN FROM TB_LMS_DSCS A WHERE A.DELYN = 'N' /* 퀴즈 */ UNION ALL SELECT 'QUIZ' AS STARE_TYPE , '퀴즈' AS TYPE_NM , A.EXAM_ID AS CODE , A.EXAM_TTL AS TTL , NVL(A.EXAM_QSTNS_CMPTNYN, 'N') AS SUBMIT_YN , A.EXAM_SDTTM AS SYMD , A.EXAM_EDTTM AS EYMD , (SELECT COUNT(C.STD_ID) FROM TB_LMS_EXAM_STARE C JOIN TB_LMS_ATNDLC_SBJCT D ON C.STD_ID = D.STD_ID AND D.ATNDLC_STSCD = 'S' WHERE C.EXAM_ID = A.EXAM_ID AND C.STARE_CNT > 0 AND D.SBJCT_ID = B.SBJCT_ID) AS JOIN_CNT , CASE WHEN A.EXAM_TYCD = 'SUBS' THEN (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM TB_LMS_ATNDLC_SBJCT WHERE SBJCT_ID = B.SBJCT_ID AND ATNDLC_STSCD = 'S' AND STD_ID IN (SELECT STD_ID FROM TB_LMS_EXAM_STARE WHERE REEXAMYN = 'Y' AND EXAM_ID = (SELECT EXAM_ID FROM TB_LMS_EXAM_BSC WHERE EXAM_SBST_REF_ID = A.EXAM_ID AND DELYN = 'N'))) ELSE (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM TB_LMS_ATNDLC_SBJCT WHERE SBJCT_ID = B.SBJCT_ID AND ATNDLC_STSCD = 'S') END AS TOTAL_CNT , (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM TB_LMS_EXAM_STARE WHERE EXAM_ID = A.EXAM_ID AND EVLYN = 'Y') AS EVAL_CNT , '' AS LATE_DTTM , A.MRK_OYN AS MRK_OYN FROM TB_LMS_EXAM_BSC A JOIN TB_LMS_EXAM_CRE_CRS_RLTN B ON A.EXAM_ID = B.EXAM_ID WHERE A.EXAM_CTGRCD = 'QUIZ' AND A.DELYN = 'N' AND B.DELYN = 'N'
AND A.EXAM_QSTNS_CMPTNYN = 'Y'
) SELECT ROW_NUMBER() OVER(ORDER BY M.SYMD) AS lineNo , A.EXAM_ID AS examCd , (SELECT CDNM FROM TB_ORG_CODE WHERE ORG_ID = A.ORG_ID AND CTGRCD = 'EXAM_STARE_UNI_CD' AND CD = A.TKEXAM_TYCD) AS examStareTypeNm , M.STARE_TYPE AS stareType , CONCAT(IF(A.EXAM_TYCD = 'EXAM', '대체', '시험'), M.TYPE_NM) AS examTypeNm , M.CODE AS code , M.TTL AS TTL , M.SUBMIT_YN AS submitYn , M.SYMD AS startDttm , M.EYMD AS endDttm , M.JOIN_CNT AS joinCnt , M.TOTAL_CNT AS totalCnt , M.EVAL_CNT AS evalCnt , M.LATE_DTTM AS lateDttm , M.MRK_OYN AS scoreOpenYn , NVL((SELECT PRD_AFTR_WRTYN FROM TB_LMS_DSCS WHERE DSCS_ID = M.CODE), 'N') AS periodAfterWriteYn FROM M JOIN TB_LMS_EXAM_BSC A ON M.CODE = A.EXAM_SBST_REF_ID JOIN TB_LMS_EXAM_CRE_CRS_RLTN B ON A.EXAM_ID = B.EXAM_ID
LEFT JOIN TB_LMS_EXAM_ABSNCE C ON A.EXAM_ID = C.EXAM_ID AND B.SBJCT_ID = C.SBJCT_ID AND C.APRV_STSCD = 'APPROVE' AND C.STD_ID = (SELECT STD_ID FROM TB_LMS_ATNDLC_SBJCT WHERE SBJCT_ID = #{crsCreCd} AND ATNDLC_STSCD <> 'D' AND USER_ID = #{userId})
WHERE A.EXAM_CTGRCD = 'EXAM' AND A.DELYN = 'N' AND B.DELYN = 'N' AND A.TKEXAM_TYCD IN ('M', 'L') AND B.SBJCT_ID = #{crsCreCd} AND A.EXAM_SBST_REF_ID IS NOT NULL
AND ((A.EXAM_TYCD = 'EXAM' AND C.STD_ID IS NOT NULL) OR A.EXAM_TYCD <> 'EXAM')

/* SQL ID : ExamDAO.listExamByEtc 설 명 : 중간/기말 수시, 외국어 시험 목록 조회 */ SELECT ROW_NUMBER() OVER(ORDER BY A.EXAM_SDTTM) AS lineNo , A.EXAM_ID AS examCd , A.TKEXAM_TYCD AS examStareTypeCd , (SELECT CDNM FROM TB_ORG_CODE WHERE ORG_ID = A.ORG_ID AND CTGRCD = 'EXAM_STARE_UNI_CD' AND CD = A.TKEXAM_TYCD) AS examStareTypeNm , A.EXAM_TTL AS examTitle , A.EXAM_SDTTM AS examStartDttm , A.EXAM_EDTTM AS examEndDttm , A.MRK_RFLTYN AS scoreAplyYn , A.MRK_OYN AS scoreOpenYn , A.MRK_OPEN_SDTTM AS scoreOpenDttm , NVL(A.EXAM_QSTNS_CMPTNYN, 'N') AS examSubmitYn , A.REEXAMYN AS reExamYn , A.EXAM_TYCD AS examTypeCd , NVL(A.MRK_RFLTRT, 0) AS scoreRatio , NVL(A.TKEXAM_MNTS, (SELECT TKEXAM_MNTS FROM TB_LMS_EXAM_BSC WHERE EXAM_ID = A.EXAM_SBST_REF_ID)) AS examStareTm , NVL((SELECT PRD_AFTR_WRTYN FROM TB_LMS_DSCS WHERE DSCS_ID = A.EXAM_SBST_REF_ID), 'N') AS periodAfterWriteYn , A.EXAM_SBST_REF_ID AS insRefCd , NVL((SELECT 'Y' FROM TB_LMS_EXAM_STARE WHERE EXAM_ID = A.EXAM_SBST_REF_ID AND STD_ID = #{stdNo} AND EDTTM IS NOT NULL), 'N') AS insJoinYn , NVL((SELECT DELYN FROM TB_LMS_EXAM_BSC WHERE EXAM_ID = A.EXAM_SBST_REF_ID), 'Y') AS insDelYn , NVL((SELECT EXAMPPR_OYN FROM TB_LMS_EXAM_BSC WHERE EXAM_ID = A.EXAM_SBST_REF_ID), 'N') AS gradeViewYn , NVL((SELECT CASE WHEN (TO_DATE(EXAM_SDTTM, 'YYYYMMDDHH24MISS') - SYSDATE) * 86400 > 0 THEN '대기' WHEN (TO_DATE(EXAM_SDTTM, 'YYYYMMDDHH24MISS') - SYSDATE) * 86400 < 0 AND (TO_DATE(EXAM_EDTTM, 'YYYYMMDDHH24MISS') - SYSDATE) * 86400 > 0 THEN '진행' WHEN (TO_DATE(EXAM_EDTTM, 'YYYYMMDDHH24MISS') - SYSDATE) * 86400 < 0 THEN '완료' END FROM TB_LMS_EXAM_BSC WHERE EXAM_ID = A.EXAM_SBST_REF_ID), '대기') AS examStatus , CASE WHEN TO_CHAR(SYSDATE, 'YYYYMMDD') = SUBSTR(A.EXAM_SDTTM, 1, 8) THEN 'Y' ELSE 'N' END AS todayYn FROM TB_LMS_EXAM_BSC A JOIN TB_LMS_EXAM_CRE_CRS_RLTN B ON A.EXAM_ID = B.EXAM_ID AND A.DELYN = 'N' AND B.DELYN = 'N' WHERE A.EXAM_CTGRCD = 'EXAM' AND B.SBJCT_ID = #{crsCreCd} AND A.TKEXAM_TYCD = #{examStareTypeCd}
AND A.EXAM_QSTNS_CMPTNYN = 'Y' AND A.USEYN = 'Y'
AND LOWER(A.EXAM_TTL) LIKE FN_LIKE_VAL(LOWER(#{searchValue}))

